{"tid":440681,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個魚拉突 咁既分組真係得啖笑","createTime":"2017-10-19T03:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T13:48:26.000Z","uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"32c0b9845dafb1880f7db7d5dcc872cd935ddedb","tid":440681,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T03:58:34.000Z","msg":"作為一個魚拉突 咁既分組真係得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n講真咁同直接宣佈曼首名有咩分別。<br />\n<br />\n令我地班魚拉突 totally no mood to 捱夜睇波 嗱,我又分析下 首先賓咩加,唔好玩啦 葡萄牙野，6分穩陣<br />\n<br />\n巴素利,,如果係巴狗就有可觀性(順便可以報上次ga仇)(不過算啦,入到決賽又會見到面) 我真係冇睇過依隊野..曼半力夠WIN,又6分<br />\n<br />\n最後一隊,我連名都唔記得 我地出青年軍練下is ok,又6分<br />\n<br />\n加上我地4大尖刀 LKK,拉車,馬達,MK 加上關鍵王連加特.. 根本場場大炒,,,,<br />\n<br />\n18分就一定..係睇下破唔破到得失球.咁一面倒ga比賽,我冇興趣,大家16強見<br />\n<br />\nP.S.比d咁ga對手魚拉突..is侮辱..哈"},{"pid":"70324289f943c4dcdfae13023f7d8a7914210793","tid":440681,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T03:59:05.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"4fe0f5361272ae59d72a8ff02b87a8a7e9d36763","tid":440681,"uid":31314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T03:59:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>.</blockquote><br />\n你老母肉酸"},{"pid":"d8387a2473783395b3539f2e9e924b19040336aa","tid":440681,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T04:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed021179ff355499f2bc29d5f4b47acc0d3187b","tid":440681,"uid":150166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:04:42.000Z","msg":"魚拉突好波！"},{"pid":"d4984546f106312bb6667e9481372dd898c916c8","tid":440681,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>.</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b2144bacbf3f40349945db2fb109e5888af0a144","tid":440681,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T06:08:35.000Z","msg":"樓豬係gay佬"},{"pid":"1043255f7d83d1adeb13f411b0de29fa14936c27","tid":440681,"uid":99861,"like